This is a very small Texture Gun Game Map. You can play this Map with 32 Players, but i thinks its better for max. 16 Players. At the Map i have put many Geometric Objects. Have Fun. And if someone put this Map on his Server, plz tell me this, i like to play my Map online with other Peoples.

Put the Skybox .vtf Files into the Skybox Folder (if the Folder doesn't exist, creat it) most on:
